{
  "stem": "4513.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I disliked hunting and fishing, mainly because my mother had sort of proselytized me [LAUGHS] in saying, look, you can't learn-- a boy cannot learn-- hunting and fishing will not cause him  to survive in this world he's in.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he's going to have to go to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He's going to have to learn to do something other than going hunting and fishing because you can't hunt and fish on these asphalt streets.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] my father-- so there was always this conflict.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father was not a person who talked an awful lot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've seen my father sit for two days without saying anything to anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just sat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, that was all-- when I went to my-- see my father's home, there were a lot of people who sat for days [LAUGHS] without saying anything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it wasn't unusual for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was rather unusual because he-- my mother would say things to him and he would sort of bow his head, shake his head, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he wasn't cruel, you know, or anything else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, he just didn't have-- he said, the only reason why you talk is when you have something to say.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He talked-- you know, the first-- my first language was French.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a crazy story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how to explain this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We spoke French as little kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, my mother finally told me one day that they learned to speak French because there was a missionary-- some missionaries who came to the reservation very early.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they learned to speak French in this little class that they had and-- from the nuns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, my mother was a Baptist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
